" Sources
" https://www.reddit.com/r/vim/comments/21f4gm/best_workflow_when_using_fugitive/
" http://michaelxavier.net/posts/2010-03-13-Git-vim-bindings-for-fugitive-vim.html
nnoremap <leader>gs :vertical G<enter>:vertical resize 120<enter>
nnoremap <leader>gd :tab G diff<enter>
nnoremap <leader>gD :tab G diff --cached<enter>
nnoremap <leader>gl :tab G log<enter>
nnoremap <leader>gc :tab G commit<enter>

nnoremap <leader>tgs :tab G<enter>
